nded, marking a transition point in the system's activity.","thinkingSignature":"bdac4eb6a7ff466a99cef22cdfe15083a22c81fa0bb568d928c20bc9729fc83d"},{"type":"text","text":"Comparing current session state against the 01:14 UTC snapshot — significant change detected (primary QLHV group session ended, new failures surfaced, stuck cron detected).\n\nSending report to group -5163901258:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g3pezk2ghkb2_1","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258","message":"🟡 Orbis-DTLX — 5p Update | 10:54 UTC 14 Apr\n\nChanges detected:\n• QLHV group (-5163901258) — **ENDED** at ~10:43 UTC — Lead session completed (DTLX BE bug fixes + API tests done, GitLab CI check delivered)\n• DTLX group (-5168104492) — **ENDED** — settings page work completed earlier\n• ⚠️ DTLX BE API tests — new failures: DTLX Full API Test v2, DTLX BE Fix & Test, DTLX BE Start & Test — all failed (500 `providerSpecificData` error, pre-existing model/provider issue, not new)\n• ⚠️ cron:ac986a8d — **STILL STUCK** — Telegram delivery retry cron running since ~10:04 UTC (~50 min), attempting to deliver to the now-ended QLHV group session\n\nPipeline: **DEGRADED** ⚠️\n• Active sessions: 3 (2× 5p crons + 1× Telegram retry cron stuck)\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n• Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\n• Blockers: ⚠️ Stuck Telegram delivery cron | ⚠️ DTLX subagent failures (model/provider errors, persistent baseline)\n\n— Orbis 🌐"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":554,"output":906,"cacheRead":43409,"cacheWrite":181,"totalTokens":45050,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776164090987,"responseId":"062d4ffc6c4ac1c1a356a7ac804a055a"}}
